data.description:
Large 5 bedroom house with split floor plan in the best school district in Lakeland! 3 car garage in gated community. Only 20 minutes to Legoland and 10 minutes to downtown Lakeland.

Living between Orlando and Clearwater beach is the best of city life, with a quiet home town feel.

12 month rental lease with First/last month and security deposit must be paid at lease signing. 

No smoking allowed inside the property.

Tenant is responsible for all utilities (to include electricity, water, and internet) and other services. Lawn care maintenance required by HOA of $150 will be included as a monthly fee.

PETS allowed with Initial fee of $250 non-refundable and a $50 monthly fee per pet. 

Tenant must abide by all HOA requirements.
